Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:15.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.07,0:19:23.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說真的 雖然不知道為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.35,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶 安藝君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.95,0:19:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冰堂同學真的和阿宅完全沒關係嗎？
